Q4 of 2025 has been nothing short of eventful, with BTC making new all time highs on October 6th, only to give back all gains on the year, and hit an alarming level of $80k earlier this morning. This 36% drawdown is nothing new for bitcoin, but coming so soon after an all time high (45 days later), is one abrupt way to end the good times. Tom Lee of Bitm
